IMAPAccount gmail
Host imap.gmail.com
User johndoe@gmail.com
AuthMechs XOAUTH2
PassCmd "~/.local/bin/oauth2get gmail johndoe@gmail.com"
SSLType IMAPS

IMAPStore gmail-remote
Account gmail

MaildirStore gmail-local
SubFolders Verbatim
# The trailing "/" is important
Path ~/.local/share/mail/gmail/
Inbox ~/.local/share/mail/gmail/Inbox

Channel gmail
Far :gmail-remote:
Near :gmail-local:
Patterns *
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *
